      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know the label says something but i've looked at it and it's so vague. i really need to get through this work day and i can't focus with this pain. if i do smaller doses like 400mg every couple hours instead of waiting 6 or 8 hours, isn't that basically the same thing just more frequent? i just want to keep a steady level in my system so it doesn't spike again.",
